info.name: API Documentation
info.description:
StartFragment

The **FoodScan API** is a robust and scalable backend service designed for the FoodScan application. It provides a comprehensive set of endpoints to manage user authentication, access food-related resources, and handle various operations efficiently. The API is built using Laravel and leverages JWT (JSON Web Tokens) for secure authentication and authorization.
